  "body": "When do you use this?  Payout annuities assume that you take money from the account on a regular schedule (every month, year, quarter, etc.) and let the rest sit there earning interest.  Compound interest: One deposit  Annuity: Many deposits.  Payout Annuity: Many withdrawals  "
