  "title": "Try It Now.",
  "body": "Try It Now  What is the probability of a z-score between -0.93 and 2.11?   Using the z-score probability table above, we can see that the probability of a value below -0.93 is .1762, and the probability of a value below 2.11 is .9826. Therefore, the probability of a value between them is .9826-.1762 = .8064   "
